@baseUrl = http://localhost:3100
@xWhatsappHost = X_ACCESS_TOKEN
@sendTo = 62xxxxx

### Root endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Connect device, use this website to view image https://jaredwinick.github.io/base64-image-viewer/
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/devices/connect
Content-Type: application/json
x-access-token: {{xWhatsappHost}}

### Restore device session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/devices/restore
Content-Type: application/json
x-access-token: {{xWhatsappHost}}


### Logout device
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/devices/disconnect
Content-Type: application/json
x-access-token: {{xWhatsappHost}}

### Send text message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/messages/text
Content-Type: application/json
x-access-token: {{xWhatsappHost}}

{
  "number": "{{sendTo}}",
  "msgid": "",
  "text": "Hello from WhatsApp API test"
}

### Send photo message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/messages/photo
Content-Type: application/json
x-access-token: {{xWhatsappHost}}

{
  "number": "{{sendTo}}",
  "url": "https://picsum.photos/200",
  "caption": "Test image",
  "viewonce": false,
  "msgid": ""
}

### Send document message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/messages/document
Content-Type: application/json
x-access-token: {{xWhatsappHost}}

{
  "number": "{{sendTo}}",
  "url": "https://www.adobe.com/support/products/enterprise/knowledgecenter/media/c4611_sample_explain.pdf",
  "caption": "Test document",
  "filename": "sample.pdf",
  "msgid": ""
}
